{
  "screen_id": "knowledge-thread",
  "route": "/knowledge/thread",
  "title": "スレッド",
  "layout": "standard",
  "notes": "c8(ui-asset-catalog.md 【最優先2】)再構築版・UI磨き第2弾(受領10)で追改修。BBS-05/10/36。GET /plaza/threads/{thread_id}(posts materialized view)+ GET /plaza/threads/{thread_id}/consensus(Polis型 Agree/Disagree/Pass 決定論投影)+ POST /plaza/stances + POST /plaza/posts を実結線。thread_id は ?thread_id= (params.thread_id)。専用ノード thread-posts が avatar(actor_id モノグラム)/actor 表示プリミティブ(display_name があれば表示・磨き第2弾#5・ihl.actor.display_name.v1)/body/引用badge(tombstone=無効引用を tone danger で明示)/相談室(dispute)導線+スレ主のみの解決マーク(round-16 OQ-PLZ-03。POST /plaza/posts への tags:['resolved'] 規約・新 Truth 型なし)を持つ。磨き第2弾#6(受領10「投稿ごとの投票ボタンに」): 賛否投票は投稿ごとのインライン Agree/Disagree/Pass ボタン(thread-posts 内・statement_id=post_id を自動送信)に統合し、旧スタンドアロン stance-form(「対象の投稿 ID」手入力)は撤去。磨き第2弾#3(受領10「『…』のなかに畳んで」): 「この投稿を相談室へ」は per-post kebab(⋮)メニューへ格納(常時露出→必要な時だけ)。返信は textarea variant。round-16 OQ-PLZ-01/02/05(昇格閾値バッジ✔/⚠の重み付き投票・カード発行委譲)は certified-breeder/primary-observer 等の actor ロール Truth データが schemas 上どこにも存在せず、ui-asset-catalog.md【最優先2】の組み立て表にも記載が無いため対象外(捏造しない・c8タスク報告に明記)。",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "shell",
      "type": "app-shell",
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "page",
          "type": "page",
          "children": [
            { "id": "title", "type": "heading", "props": { "text_key": "knowledge-thread.title.text", "text": "スレッド", "level": 1 } },
            {
              "id": "head",
              "type": "card",
              "props": {
                "source_path": "/api/v1/plaza/threads/{{params.thread_id}}",
                "bind_text": "話題: {{topic}}（チャンネル {{channel}}）"
              }
            },
            { "id": "posts-title", "type": "heading", "props": { "text_key": "knowledge-thread.posts-title.text", "text": "投稿", "level": 2 } },
            {
              "id": "posts-rich",
              "type": "thread-posts",
              "props": { "empty_text": "まだ投稿がありません。" }
            },
            { "id": "consensus-title", "type": "heading", "props": { "text_key": "knowledge-thread.consensus-title.text", "text": "合意の可視化(Polis型)", "level": 2 } },
            {
              "id": "consensus-table",
              "type": "table",
              "props": {
                "source_path": "/api/v1/plaza/threads/{{params.thread_id}}/consensus",
                "bind_items": "data.consensus-table.statements",
                "columns": [
                  { "key": "statement_id", "label": "論点(投稿ID)" },
                  { "key": "agree", "label": "賛成" },
                  { "key": "disagree", "label": "反対" },
                  { "key": "pass", "label": "保留" },
                  { "key": "consensus", "label": "合意", "cell": "badge", "tone": "success", "true_label": "✔ 合意", "false_label": "—" },
                  { "key": "divisive", "label": "対立", "cell": "badge", "tone": "caution", "true_label": "⚠ 対立", "false_label": "—" }
                ],
                "empty_text": "まだ賛否の投票がありません。"
              }
            },
            { "id": "reply-title", "type": "heading", "props": { "text": "返信する", "level": 2 } },
            {
              "id": "reply-form",
              "type": "form",
              "action": { "kind": "api", "method": "POST", "path": "/api/v1/plaza/posts" },
              "props": {
                "static": {
                  "channel": "{{data.head.channel}}",
                  "topic": "{{data.head.topic}}",
                  "board_kind": "{{data.head.posts.0.board_kind}}",
                  "thread_id": "{{params.thread_id}}"
                }
              },
              "children": [
                { "id": "reply-body", "type": "field", "props": { "name": "body", "label": "返信本文", "variant": "textarea", "required": true } },
                { "id": "reply-submit", "type": "button", "props": { "type": "submit", "label": "返信する", "variant": "primary" } }
              ]
            },
            {
              "id": "back-board",
              "type": "link",
              "props": { "label_key": "knowledge-thread.back-board.label", "label": "掲示板へ戻る", "href": "/s/knowledge-board" }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "transitions": [
    { "from": "reply-form", "to_screen_id": "knowledge-thread", "label": "返信後に再読込" }
  ]
}
